      • fromVoidCallback

        public static <T,FluentT extends ResourceT,ResourceT,FluentImplT extends CreatableImpl<FluentT,T,FluentImplT,ResourceT>> ServiceCallback<T> fromVoidCallback(FluentImplT modelImpl,
                                                                                                                                                             ServiceCallback<Void> callback)
        Creates a callback returning the inner resource from a fluent model and a void callback, and set the inner on the fluent model.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the inner resource type
        FluentT - the fluent resource type
        ResourceT - the fluent model base type that all fluent models in the same task group derive from
        FluentImplT - the implementation for the fluent resource type
        Parameters:
        modelImpl - the implementation instance of the fluent resource
        callback - the void callback
        Returns:
        new callback from the void callback
